<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٣٤٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/484">‌أَحْمَدُ بْنُ حَنْبَلٍ، </a>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">‌يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6092">‌مِسْعَرٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5419">‌مُحَارِبِ بْنِ دِثَارٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">‌جَابِرَ بْنَ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٥٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ لِي عَلَى النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ دَيْنٌ فَقَضَانِي وَزَادَنِي.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>